  <h1 class='post_title'>Dropify</h1>
  <a href='http://www.dropify.herokuapp.com'>www.dropify.herokuapp.com</a>
  <p>Dropify is a mobile-first web application that allows users to 'drop' messages and photos in their current location to be later found by others. Wander around a city and discover experiences and memories left by other Dropify users or, as an advertiser, pay to leave featured content in any location.
    <br><br>
  Dropify was created for the Salesforce.com 'Dreamforce' 48-hour Hackathon and uses Rails as a back-end API with a thick HTML5/Javascript mobile client. Google Maps was implemented for both geolocation and to provide a richer user experience, whilst Stripe was used to allow advertisers to pay for featured content.</p>
